              <B><font color='#FF3300' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='2'>It's Been So Long....<BR></B></font><font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='1'>2002-07-16 21:53:52&nbsp;-&nbsp;<font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='1'><I>Main Tankin' Pussy Numero Uno</I>&nbsp;              </font><br>
              <img src="images/content_bar.jpg" width="645" height="1"></p>
            <p>
<font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='2'>		
Well, there really hasn't been a damn thing to post lately. I don't generally like to post repeat kill shots on every mob in the game, over and over and over and over again, ad nauseum. <br />
<br />
Yea, we've been farming. It's been gay. There hasn't been a patch to EQ to fix VT loot, VT gayness, or general game gayness in like, 2-3 months. It's basically EQ Stasis at the moment.<br />
<br />
Fortunately, we've had some heated debates over the usual crap that comes about when people go stir crazy over a lack of content, class balance issues, epics, etc... etc...<br />
<br />
Anywaysss... I'm gonna go ahead and spoil the Emperor encounter for you guys. Check this shit out:<br />
